        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>Ego <persName key="#Princeps #childOf" ref="#people/3022"
                            >Iordanus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Princeps">princeps</rs>
                        <rs key="#childOf">filius</rs> domni <persName key="#Princeps #parentOf"
                            ref="#people/3002">Iordani</persName>
                        <rs key="#Princeps">principis</rs>, dico et promitto tibi domno <persName
                            key="#Cardinals #Abbots" ref="#people/4222">ODERISIO</persName>
                        <rs key="#Cardinals">cardinali</rs> et <rs key="#Abbots">abbati</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/84">casinensis</orgName>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>, quod ab hac die in antea ero tibi
                        per fidem amicus absque fraude et malo ingenio, et non ero in facto nec in
                        consilio ut vitam aut membra perdas, aut aliquo ingenio sis captus ad tuam
                        damnietatem. Abbatiam et honorem quem hodie habes, non ero in facto aut in
                        consilio aut in consensu ut eum perdas. et totam terram Sancti Benedicti cum
                            <rs key="#Fortress">castellis</rs> et pertinentiis et <rs key="#Villas"
                            >villis</rs> suis, sicut <rs key="#Imperial/royal_diploma">precepta
                            imperialia</rs> domni <persName ref="#people/14">Karoli</persName>,
                            <persName ref="#people/173">Ottonis</persName>, <persName
                            ref="#people/130">Enrici</persName>, et <persName ref="#people/261"
                            >Chorradi</persName> continent; per <rs key="#Fines">fines</rs> et
                        terminos suos, Insuper et <rs key="#Fortress">castella</rs> quae postea per
                        concessionem, sive per <rs key="#Commutatio">cambium</rs>, a domno <persName
                            key="#Princeps #grandparentOf" ref="#people/3001">Richardo</persName>
                        <rs key="#Princeps">principe</rs>
                        <rs key="#grandparentOf">avo</rs> meo; monasterio Sancti Benedicti addita
                        sunt. id est, <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Fortress"
                            ref="#places/4512">Mortula</placeName>. <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Fortress"
                            ref="#places/5145">Sanctus Salvator, de cucuruzzo</placeName>.
                            <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Fortress"
                            ref="#places/4519">Fracte</placeName>, et <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Fortress"
                            ref="#places/4514">Terame</placeName>, cum omnibus suis pertinentiis.
                        sicut precepta quae predictus avus meus una cum Iordane principe <rs
                            key="#parentOf">patre</rs> meo fecit; continere videntur. et <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Fortress"
                            ref="#places/4523">pedem de monte</placeName> quod a parte Sancti
                        Benedicti, in concambio receptum est. a <rs key="#Count">comite</rs>
                        <persName key="#Count" ref="#people/5039">adenulfo</persName>. <rs
                            key="#Fortress">Castellum</rs> de <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Fortress"
                            ref="#places/4526">Suio</placeName> cum pertinentiis suis ex utraque
                        parte <rs key="#Rivers">fluminis</rs>, sicut <persName ref="#people/5040"
                            >Goffredus monius</persName> tenuit illud, quando Iordanus princeps
                        pater meus tenebat <rs key="#Cities">civitatem</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Cities" ref="#places/571">suessam</placeName>. <rs
                            key="#Fortress">Castrum</rs>
                        <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Fortress"
                            ref="#places/4537">pontecurvo</placeName> cum pertinentiis suis sicut
                            <persName key="#Princeps #siblingOf" ref="#people/3010"
                            >Richardus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Princeps">princeps</rs>
                        <rs key="#siblingOf">frater</rs> meus et <persName ref="#people/2422"
                            key="#Count">Robertus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Count">comes</rs> concesserunt, et firmaverunt illud Sancto
                        Benedicto. Istas et omnes alias terras, castella videlicet cum pertinentiis
                        eorum; et villas quas hodie habes et dominaris; ac tenes. per te vel homines
                        tuos, aut in antea cum consilio meo acquisieris, sicut ab antecessoribus
                        meis principibus, monasterio Sancti Benedicti, et tibi, atque antecessoribus
                        tuis concessa fuit; et per sacramentum confirmata. Haec inquam omnia non ero
                        in facto neque in consilio, ut monasterium Sancti Benedicti, et tu ea
                        perdas. sed contra omnes homines qui ea vobis tollere quesierint. Adjuvabo
                        te et monasterium Sancti Benedicti ad ea tenendum et defendendum ad honorem
                        et proficuum suprascripti monasterii. Omnia haec observabo tibi tuisque
                        successoribus, per bonam fidem sine fraude et malo ingenio. sic me deus
                        adjuvet et haec sancta Evangelia. Hoc actum est in capitulo casinensis
                        monasterii, fratribus universis coram positis, et baronibus principis,
                        videlicet his. <persName key="#Witness #Count #childOf" ref="#people/5041"
                            >Adenulfus</persName> comes <rs key="#childOf">filius</rs>
                        <persName key="#Count" ref="#people/5039">adenulfi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Count">comitis</rs>. <persName key="#Witness" ref="#people/5042"
                            >Enricus de bolita</persName>. <persName key="#Witness"
                            ref="#people/4265">Manso</persName> et <persName
                            key="#Witness #siblingOf"><name ref="Landulfus"
                            >Landulfus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#siblingOf">frater</rs> ejus. <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Abner f. Turstaini">Abner filius tristaini.</name></persName>
                        Fuit etiam ibi <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Pandulfus de Sexto"
                                >pandulfus de sexto</name></persName>. et <persName key="#Witness"
                                ><name ref="Iordanus Pinzasta">Iordanis pinzasta</name></persName>.
                        et <persName key="#Witness" ref="#people/4250">Paldi de benafro</persName>.
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Pandulfus de Fracte">Pandulfus de
                                fracte</name></persName>. et alii plures <rs key="#Witness #milesOf"
                            >milites</rs> et <rs key="#Witness #Boni_viri/boni_homines">boni
                            homines</rs>. Anno dominice incarnationis, Millesimo centesimo vicesimo
                        tertio. Mense Iunio. indictione prima. </ab>
                </div>
            </div>
